 reproductive coercion and women&rsquo;s contraceptive decision making, mitigating barriers to help-seeking for survivors of IPV, and exploring innovative intervention strategies for male IPV perpetrators. Dr. Holliday applies a mixed-methods approach, including participatory research methods like concept mapping.</p>    <h2><a id="mchn"></a>Interview</h2>			<p>Click below to listen to Charvonne Holliday's story as  an MCH leader in academe.</p>            <button class="accordion">Career focus: doctoral dissertation</button>        <div class="panel">          <div class="vidwrap">          <iframe src="https://player.vimeo.com/video/520116151" width="640" height="360" frameborder="0" allow="autoplay; fullscreen" allowfullscreen></iframe>          </div>        </div>              <button class="accordion">Career focus on MCH</button>        <div class="panel">          <div class="vidwrap">          <iframe src="https://player.vimeo.com/video/520116374" width="640" height="360" frameborder="0" allow="autoplay; fullscreen" allowfullscreen></iframe>          </div>        </div>        <button class="accordion">Uniqueness of doctoral fellowship at university</button>        <div class="panel">          <div class="vidwrap">          <iframe src="https://player.vimeo.com/video/520116232" width="640" height="360" frameborder="0" allow="autoplay; fullscreen" allowfullscreen></iframe>          </div>        </div>     <button class="accordion">Exposure to Title V, MCHB, AMCHP, etc.</button>        <div class="panel">          <div class="vidwrap">          <iframe src="https://player.vimeo.com/video/520116284" width="640" height="360" frameborder="0" allow="autoplay; fullscreen" allowfullscreen></iframe>          </div>        </div>        <button class="accordion">Connecting at Center of Excellence Catalyst meetings</button>        <div class="panel">          <div class="vidwrap">          <iframe src="https://player.vimeo.com/video/5